{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bfc24d736e","title":"省、市委书记会议上各同志提出的问题","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"960743b61c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":25,"articleId":"bfc24d736e"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7fc5fd78be","name":"中共中央办公厅"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"53e755c8cc","type":"title","text":"省、市委书记会议上各同志提出的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"4a39968435","type":"authors","text":"中共中央办公厅","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"1440cadeac","type":"appellation","text":"李富春：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"f506a9a095","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）应当从过去四年的经验中，好好地研究今后农业经费的使用，怎样才能够得到最快和最好的效果。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"808bc56959","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）应当着手进行海南岛、云南、新疆、甘肃走廊、内蒙古等地的发展农业的规划。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"d3e88ff76d","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）今年的增产节约应当着重搞好各种指标、定额和制度。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"ad3903f60e","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）劳动力的安排，过去是分“口”管理，造成了很大混乱，建议中央指定适当部门加以统一筹划。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"8c8edd4c2b","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）集体消费的标准如何降低，个人消费的比例（如工人、农民、士兵、学生之间）怎样才算合理，应当全盘地进行研究。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"1c62317c03","type":"appellation","text":"林祖：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"642a84e32b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）小学、初中的毕业生现在和将来都是小部分升学、大部分参加生产；高中的毕业生现在是大部分升学、小部参加生产。针对这种情况，应当对学生和学生家长进行劳动教育和前途教育。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"dcb41cba31","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）应当改变现在的抽调干部投考高等学校的办法，今后仍然允许干部自由投考，但是学习期间应当不给工资，只给一般的助学金。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"5db516207c","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）■■■中等技术学校的毕业生投考高等学校。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"9bd85a28b5","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）城市的小学和初中的毕业生参加生产比农村有更多的困难，因此，城市的初中和高中应该比农村多招一些学生。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"d458962f4f","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）初中、高中毕业生有的省多，有的省少，建议各省自行■■。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"329e118015","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）建议各地方在群众自愿和可能的条件下，推广农村小学民办或民办公助的办法。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"c90f6a26ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）建议抽调一些政治上比较强的老干部，到学校当政治教员，现在在校的老干部应该讲政治课。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"0a56cd18d8","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）各类学校的助学金制度很混乱，应该加以整理。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"50dc296f94","type":"paragraph","text":"（九）中等技术学校很多，质量不高，希望各省市帮助有关部门加以整理。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"6feeb8588d","type":"paragraph","text":"（十）希望各部门、各省市在这次整编中抽调一批好的干部到文教系统去工作。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"1adfa88d53","type":"appellation","text":"贾拓夫：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"0f267d3b23","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）希望各省加强对棉花收购工作的领导，提高棉花的收购量。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"4f26fe2120","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）希望各省多搞一些小型煤矿，增加民用煤的供应量。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"94ba1f3bf9","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）希望中央各工业部分别同地方有关的部门建立密切的联系，统一安排各行各业的生产、销售和原料供应的计划。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"c48015c461","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）希望各地安排今年工业生产的时候，特别注意合营的小厂和手工业，不要把它们遗漏掉。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"},{"id":"f0c9773492","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅机要室　　一九五七年一月二十七日发","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e"}],"page":{"id":"0da6844ba2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bfc24d736e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}